des:
Alexa and the Smart Security products work together to help you control Smart Security and home appliance nice and easy.

There’s no need to go to the panel to arm and disarm - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. 
After connecting Alexa to your Smart Security products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Smart Security" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Smart Security account in our "Smart Security" app;
(3). You need to have some Smart Security devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Smart Security" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Smart Security" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Smart Security" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Smart Security", and you'll be navigated to login page;
(9). Input your account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on light"
“Alexa, turn off light"
